{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act31side", "eventName": "懷黍離", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "HS-8", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "種因", "storyInfo": "在一片混沌裡，年、夕、黍三人都要重新直面那個問題：“我是誰？”\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$chenandwei_intro", "key": "$chenandwei_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_gateopen"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "暗無天日。"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不知地深幾許，沒有半點陽光透進來，空氣也凝重得彷彿能感受到穹頂的重量。"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是一座陵墓。"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#8$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼情況……我回這來了？", "name": "年"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#8$1"}, {"id": 18, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喂，老東西，還活著嗎？我來看看你啦。", "name": "年"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#1$1"}, {"id": 20, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_gintcrturnhle"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（喑啞的嘶吼）", "name": "低沉的聲音"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#1$1"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "眼前是一扇厚重的大門，聲音是從門後傳來的。"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "睡了這麼久，火氣是半點都沒少啊……", "name": "年"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#1$1"}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別裝模作樣嚇唬人了，在這裡躺了這麼長時間，你真的還剩下什麼能耐嗎？", "name": "年"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#1$1"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼……", "name": "年"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#6$1"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒什麼好怕的……吧。", "name": "年"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#6$1"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "25_g06_mountainroad_d", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_gatecloz"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowstormflp", "volume": 0.6, "loop": "true", "channel": "bgs"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#8$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "尚蜀？", "name": "年"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#8$1"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是哪座山頭，怎麼連塊路牌都沒有……不對，這是哪一年？", "name": "年"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#8$1"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看這路上兩邊的房子，像是沒有移動地塊的樣子……怎麼像是我剛來尚蜀的時候？", "name": "年"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#8$1"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "叮——噹——"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一人正用繩子將自己懸在陡峭的山崖上，用一錘一鑿在懸壁上刻下一行行字。"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喂——山上那兄弟，你做什麼呢？", "name": "年"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#1$1"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1245_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你不認識我？！", "name": "土木天師"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1245_1#1$1"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我為什麼要認識你？", "name": "年"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#5$1"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1245_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這整座尚蜀城都是在我的設計下建造出來的！", "name": "土木天師"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1245_1#1$1"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喔，厲害厲害。", "name": "年"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#1$1"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1245_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "天災就要來了，人都已經撤走了。但我建造的這些屋子，都要毀於這場天災。", "name": "土木天師"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1245_1#1$1"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不甘心！", "name": "土木天師"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1245_1#1$1"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "靖炎五年，餘至尚蜀，歷三十載……《尚蜀城記》？", "name": "年"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#8$1"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1245_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我要把我建造這座城的過程全部刻在這山崖上，讓後世億兆百姓全部記得我的功績！", "name": "土木天師"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1245_1#1$1"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是天災馬上就要來了哎，就算你不惜命，一道天雷劈下來，這座山頭都不一定保得住，你這不是白費功夫？", "name": "年"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#8$1"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1245_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "管不了那麼多了，我就只有這一個方法。要是沒人知道我的作為，我還不如不活了！", "name": "土木天師"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1245_1#1$1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哪有這樣的人……好吧，你接著忙，我就不打擾啦。", "name": "年"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#5$1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喂，山上這條路最後通到哪裡啊？", "name": "年"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#1$1"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1245_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不知道。", "name": "土木天師"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1245_1#1$1"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_indoor", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_gatecloz"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#8$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是你……", "name": "年"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#8$1"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "懇請先生賜劍。", "name": "盲眼的少年劍客"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要劍，做什麼？", "name": "年"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#8$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "救人，報仇。", "name": "盲眼的少年劍客"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我說過，我鑄的劍很貴的，你用什麼換？", "name": "年"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#1$1"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的命。", "name": "盲眼的少年劍客"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "又來……", "name": "年"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#8$1"}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我應該已經拒絕你了。", "name": "年"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#8$1"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "盲眼的少年劍客"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你記不記恨我，當年用一把破銅爛鐵就打發了你？", "name": "年"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#7$1"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我在說什麼，不過是個幻影。", "name": "年"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#6$1"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是您偏偏還記得我。", "name": "盲眼的少年劍客"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是惦記著電影劇本的原型故事……還是忍不住會想，要是當時真的送你一把好劍，故事結局會不會有什麼不一樣。", "name": "年"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#6$1"}, {"id": 113, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "像您這樣神通廣大、見識無數的人，又怎會對我這樣的無名之輩抱有惻隱之心呢？", "name": "盲眼的少年劍客"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "區區一個人類的命，對您來說，確實太不值錢了。", "name": "盲眼的少年劍客"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也不能說得這麼過分吧，我還是很喜歡你們人類的。", "name": "年"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#7$1"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您看我們，就像在看戲。", "name": "盲眼的少年劍客"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您的隨性之舉，就能為這齣戲添一處奇景，改變無數人的命運。到興起的時候，您甚至也想加入進來，唱上幾句。", "name": "盲眼的少年劍客"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可戲裡風景千萬，唯獨您不在戲中。", "name": "盲眼的少年劍客"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您始終孤身一人。", "name": "盲眼的少年劍客"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真是，看走馬燈這件事也能落到我的身上……", "name": "年"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#2$1"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "累了，這把劍是認真打的，你帶走吧。", "name": "年"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#7$1"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就讓我看看，故事結局還有沒有什麼變數。", "name": "年"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#7$1"}, {"id": 128, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "先生，有一個少年，託我一定在今年冬至日前，把這個包裹交給您。", "name": "老人"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他不敢親自來見我？", "name": "年"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#8$1"}, {"id": 138, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他應該，已經死了……", "name": "老人"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "包裹是空的。"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "年"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#6$1"}, {"id": 143, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 3.0, "xstrength": 20.0, "ystrength": 20.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_collapse"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "國蝕器鏽，如夢似電，無蹤泡影。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "25_g11_yanroom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$dooropenquite"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$midautumn", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_2015_dusk_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_2015_dusk_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是……？", "name": "夕"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2015_dusk_1#9$1"}, {"id": 168, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_799_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "先生，在下恭候多時了。", "name": "阮先生"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_799_1#1$1"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_2015_dusk_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等我？", "name": "夕"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2015_dusk_1#9$1"}, {"id": 175, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_799_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在下有一事不解，請先生解惑。", "name": "阮先生"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_799_1#1$1"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_2015_dusk_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說來聽聽。", "name": "夕"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2015_dusk_1#1$1"}, {"id": 179, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_799_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "先生，今日我到城郊採風，見到河邊棲著一隻奇異的羽獸。", "name": "阮先生"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_799_1#1$1"}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我從來沒看過那麼漂亮的羽獸……我正要掏出紙筆來畫，它卻振翅一飛，消失不見了。", "name": "阮先生"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_799_1#1$1"}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我再想憑記憶裡的印象去描繪它，卻無論如何畫不出來了。", "name": "阮先生"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_799_1#1$1"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_2015_dusk_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "力所不及的事，過去便過去吧。", "name": "夕"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2015_dusk_1#1$1"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_799_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對其他人來說，過去也就過去了。可我姑且還自詡是個畫家……是畫家，總還是想留下點什麼的。", "name": "阮先生"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_799_1#1$1"}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些年來，也畫了不少。總覺得只有畫得夠多，見過的風景夠多，才算不枉這一生。", "name": "阮先生"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_799_1#1$1"}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可我終於想明白了一個道理……畫，到底是死物。", "name": "阮先生"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_799_1#1$1"}, {"id": 189, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_2015_dusk_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是何意？", "name": "夕"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2015_dusk_1#9$1"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_799_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "此時畫下的風景，下一瞬便是過眼雲煙。畫得越多，越覺得自己的畫微不足道。", "name": "阮先生"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_799_1#1$1"}, {"id": 193, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_2015_dusk_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這不是理所當然的事？", "name": "夕"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2015_dusk_1#1$1"}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "人生年不滿百，想看遍這片大地只能是奢望。", "name": "夕"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2015_dusk_1#1$1"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_799_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不……先生應該還是沒有明白。", "name": "阮先生"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_799_1#1$1"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡有在下一幅拙作，還想請先生指點一二。", "name": "阮先生"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_799_1#1$1"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_hgsldpn"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_lungmen_m", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "25_g05_mountaincity_d", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "35_g1_yumenstreet_d", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_battlefield", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_2015_dusk_1#9$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是畫？", "name": "夕"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2015_dusk_1#9$1"}, {"id": 223, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_799_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是我的畫。", "name": "阮先生"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_799_1#1$1"}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是我們肉眼凡胎，凡夫俗子，所見風景。", "name": "阮先生"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_799_1#1$1"}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就算是您這樣的先生，您所行所見的風景，比起這片大地千年間天翻地覆的變化，也不過是滄海一粟罷了。", "name": "阮先生"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_799_1#1$1"}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "先生，再好好看看吧。", "name": "阮先生"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_799_1#1$1"}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們都只有這一夕的時間了。", "name": "阮先生"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_799_1#1$1"}, {"id": 229, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_hgsldpn"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "47_g10_fairyfarmland_ex", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "筆輟卷闔，如痴似醉，一夕燼盡。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$newhope01_intro", "key": "$newhope01_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1242_1#9$1", "duration": 1.0, "bstart": 0.1, "bend": 0.25}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "長得真好……", "name": "面目模糊的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1242_1#9$1"}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些都是你種的嗎？", "name": "面目模糊的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1242_1#9$1"}, {"id": 247, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2025_shu_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是這裡的人們種的。", "name": "黍"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#1$1"}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就像你說的，我不能用我的能力來干涉這些莊稼的生長……總有一天我會消失不見的，但這裡的人們還要生活很久。", "name": "黍"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#1$1"}, {"id": 253, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1242_1#9$1", "bstart": 0.1, "bend": 0.25}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真是辛苦你了……", "name": "面目模糊的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1242_1#9$1"}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好久不見，黍。", "name": "面目模糊的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1242_1#9$1"}, {"id": 256, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2025_shu_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真奇怪，我那個弟弟也說，最近總會夢見你。", "name": "黍"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#2$1"}, {"id": 258, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1242_1#9$1", "bstart": 0.1, "bend": 0.25}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "幹嘛總是要惦記我呢……是不是人上了年紀，就容易懷念過去了？", "name": "面目模糊的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1242_1#9$1"}, {"id": 260, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2025_shu_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你也會開我玩笑了。", "name": "黍"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#9$1"}, {"id": 262, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "生活在這裡的人，都記得曾經有一位“神農”，總結了二十四節氣，教給人們耕種的知識。還冒著生命危險，把萬頃凍土開墾成良田。", "name": "黍"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#9$1"}, {"id": 263, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1242_1#2$1", "bstart": 0.1, "bend": 0.25}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“神農”，我怎麼擔得起呢。明明是我們一起做過的事，你怎麼好全推在我身上？", "name": "面目模糊的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1242_1#2$1"}, {"id": 265, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2025_shu_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "過去這麼久了，還分什麼你我嗎？", "name": "黍"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#9$1"}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只記得，在我像一個孩子一樣漫無目的地遊蕩的時候，有一個人把我留在了身邊，給了我一個“家”。", "name": "黍"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#9$1"}, {"id": 268, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2025_shu_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她告訴我，不必在意什麼人獸有別。我可以……我應該像一個人一樣活著。", "name": "黍"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#8$1"}, {"id": 270, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1242_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.1, "bend": 0.25}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可我沒有想到，你還留在這裡。", "name": "面目模糊的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1242_1#1$1"}, {"id": 272, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2025_shu_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是我答應過你的。守護好這片土地，讓更多的人能吃飽飯。", "name": "黍"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#1$1"}, {"id": 274, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1242_1#5$1", "bstart": 0.1, "bend": 0.25}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "黍啊……你怨過我嗎？", "name": "面目模糊的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1242_1#5$1"}, {"id": 276, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2025_shu_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "黍"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#8$1"}, {"id": 278, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1242_1#5$1", "bstart": 0.1, "bend": 0.25}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一千年了，哪裡談得上是奉獻呢？這明明是囚禁……", "name": "面目模糊的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1242_1#5$1"}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哪怕你已經神識散盡，還要因為與這片土地的連結被困在這裡，不得自由。", "name": "面目模糊的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1242_1#5$1"}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因為我犯下的一個錯……", "name": "面目模糊的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1242_1#5$1"}, {"id": 282, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2025_shu_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不會怨你……我只怨自己，最後沒有替你去那趟北邊的遠行。", "name": "黍"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#1$1"}, {"id": 284, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1242_1#2$1", "bstart": 0.1, "bend": 0.25}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "黍……你知道的，與你認識這麼長時間，我從來沒有一刻把你當作“神”，我甚至都快忘了這一回事。", "name": "面目模糊的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1242_1#2$1"}, {"id": 286, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可直到最後與你分別的時候，我才意識到，我是有私心的，作為“人”的私心。", "name": "面目模糊的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1242_1#2$1"}, {"id": 287, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1242_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.1, "bend": 0.25}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想懇求你留下來，繼續幫助這裡的人們。我的無數同族，他們都需要你。", "name": "面目模糊的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1242_1#1$1"}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可我不確定，你會不會愛他們，就像對我一樣……", "name": "面目模糊的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1242_1#1$1"}, {"id": 290, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2025_shu_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恐怕，我讓你失望了。", "name": "黍"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#4$1"}, {"id": 292, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1242_1#2$1", "bstart": 0.1, "bend": 0.25}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們還是失敗了，對嗎？", "name": "面目模糊的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1242_1#2$1"}, {"id": 294, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2025_shu_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "黍"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#8$1"}, {"id": 296, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2025_shu_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你最後還是沒有找到種子，我也沒能研究出可以種在源石土壤上的莊稼。", "name": "黍"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#1$1"}, {"id": 298, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2025_shu_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "連這片土地，我們都沒能保護下來。", "name": "黍"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#3$1"}, {"id": 300, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1242_1#6$1", "bstart": 0.1, "bend": 0.25}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "人定勝天……人甚麼時候真的勝過天呢？", "name": "面目模糊的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1242_1#6$1"}, {"id": 302, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1242_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.1, "bend": 0.25}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "黍……你後悔嗎？", "name": "面目模糊的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1242_1#1$1"}, {"id": 304, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2025_shu_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "黍"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#1$1"}, {"id": 306, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1242_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.1, "bend": 0.25}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我說的這些，其實你早都知道的，對嗎？", "name": "面目模糊的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1242_1#1$1"}, {"id": 308, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2025_shu_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的，我都知道。", "name": "黍"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#1$1"}, {"id": 310, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1242_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.1, "bend": 0.25}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你本不該在這裡見到我……", "name": "面目模糊的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1242_1#1$1"}, {"id": 312, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你只是殘留在這個裝置裡的一縷意識，我是這一點意識的回憶。罔兩問景，多麼悲哀。", "name": "面目模糊的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1242_1#1$1"}, {"id": 313, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2025_shu_1#1$1", "duration": 2.0, "bstart": 0.2, "bend": 0.3}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我就是你。", "name": "面目模糊的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#1$1"}, {"id": 317, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_dripink"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_143#2", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_143#1", "action": "jump", "posto": "0,0", "power": 20.0, "times": 1.0, "duration": 0.3}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_143#1", "duration": 0.0}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘎——？", "name": "奇妙的生物"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_143#1"}, {"id": 330, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_cottage", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_2015_dusk_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你還在這裡。", "name": "夕"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2015_dusk_1#1$1"}, {"id": 340, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_143#1"}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我一直在你心裡。", "name": "“自在”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_143#1"}, {"id": 342, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_2015_dusk_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "命犯貪嗔，貪生怕死。", "name": "夕"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2015_dusk_1#2$1"}, {"id": 344, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_2015_dusk_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我都差點忘了，當時為什麼會畫你出來。", "name": "夕"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2015_dusk_1#1$1"}, {"id": 346, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "山高水遙無是處，無礙吾自在人間。", "name": "夕"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2015_dusk_1#1$1"}, {"id": 347, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "渾渾噩噩了許久，我竟然連這點清醒都丟了。", "name": "夕"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2015_dusk_1#1$1"}, {"id": 348, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "誰說要畫遍世間萬物才算畫家，畫出一山一水，便是一山一水的境界。", "name": "夕"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2015_dusk_1#1$1"}, {"id": 349, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_watersubcreate", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_xsplashink"}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 2.0, "keep": "true", "initamount": 0.0, "amount": 1.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "畫家揮劍，層山盡起。"}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我即為我。"}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我見即萬象。"}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.0, "amount": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_corridor", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喂，醒醒？", "name": "炎熔"}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_1011_purgatory_1#1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在片場睡過去，作為導演也太失職了吧。", "name": "炎熔"}, "figure_art": "char_1011_purgatory_1#1"}, {"id": 371, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "睏了就睡嘛……我們現在拍的是哪一部？", "name": "年"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#7$1"}, {"id": 373, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_1011_purgatory_1#1"}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "《機械巨獸大戰巨獸》。", "name": "炎熔"}, "figure_art": "char_1011_purgatory_1#1"}, {"id": 375, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喔，這不是我壓箱底的劇本嗎。", "name": "年"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#5$1"}, {"id": 377, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_1011_purgatory_1#1"}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是指離譜程度嗎……", "name": "炎熔"}, "figure_art": "char_1011_purgatory_1#1"}, {"id": 379, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我發誓，今年一定是最後一年了。", "name": "炎熔"}, "figure_art": "char_1011_purgatory_1#1"}, {"id": 380, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嬉笑怒罵，皆成文章，傳說志異，都是故事……", "name": "年"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#7$1"}, {"id": 382, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我說，小炎熔啊。", "name": "年"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#7$1"}, {"id": 383, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……你為什麼願意陪我鬧這麼久？", "name": "年"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#7$1"}, {"id": 384, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_1011_purgatory_1#1"}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你答應我的傳奇武器，什麼時候給我？", "name": "炎熔"}, "figure_art": "char_1011_purgatory_1#1"}, {"id": 386, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你果然還是惦記這個……", "name": "年"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#1$1"}, {"id": 388, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要是哪天，我消失得無影無蹤，再也找不到——你會想我嗎？", "name": "年"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#7$1"}, {"id": 390, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_1011_purgatory_1#1"}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不會。", "name": "炎熔"}, "figure_art": "char_1011_purgatory_1#1"}, {"id": 392, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真有那麼一天，不會有人記得你。", "name": "炎熔"}, "figure_art": "char_1011_purgatory_1#1"}, {"id": 393, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你造出來的武器，工具，城市，還有那些電影，全都會消失不見……你明知道這一點。", "name": "炎熔"}, "figure_art": "char_1011_purgatory_1#1"}, {"id": 394, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說得對……我也不該在這裡見到你。", "name": "年"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#7$1"}, {"id": 396, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_1011_purgatory_1#1"}}, {"id": 397, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "炎熔"}, "figure_art": "char_1011_purgatory_1#1"}, {"id": 398, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 399, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊，說得沒錯。我折騰的這些玩意，說到底都是白費功夫。可忍不住，就是要找點樂子，留點念想。", "name": "年"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#6$1"}, {"id": 400, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "東西留過，我也開心過，這就夠了。", "name": "年"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#6$1"}, {"id": 401, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 402, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝謝你啊，小炎熔。在羅德島上有你陪著胡鬧的這些日子，還挺開心的。", "name": "年"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#1$1"}, {"id": 403, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 404, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_1011_purgatory_1#1"}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 406, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 407, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 408, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 409, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "丟臉……明明是自己造出來的東西，還要反過來教訓我一番。", "name": "年"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#6$1"}, {"id": 410, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 411, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "動不動讓別人翻些無關緊要的記憶，實在是件很矯情的事……", "name": "年"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#2$1"}, {"id": 412, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_magic_3"}}, {"id": 413, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 414, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 415, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 416, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 417, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 418, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 419, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "夠了吧，能從那團混沌中分出來，我們已經回答過那個問題了。", "name": "年"}}, {"id": 420, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是一顆心臟而已，就別妄想再收我們回去了。", "name": "年"}}, {"id": 421, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老傢伙，我們辛辛苦苦從暗無天日的陵墓裡走出來，不是為了繼續活在你的陰影下的。", "name": "年"}}, {"id": 422, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "給我——", "name": "年"}}, {"id": 423, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 424, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 425, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$glass"}}, {"id": 426, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_white", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 427, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "text": "<color=#000000>破去——</color>", "x": 290.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.001, "width": 700.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 428, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.05}}, {"id": 429, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 430, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1"}}, {"id": 431, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st2", "text": "破去——", "x": 290.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.001, "width": 700.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 432, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st2"}}, {"id": 433, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 434, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 435, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 436, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 437, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 438, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 439, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}